<bug>
    <id>3731</id>
    <title>Virtual keyboard is not dismissed in site settings</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">PR https://github.com/wordpress-mobile/WordPress-Android/pull/3719 introduced a new issue, where the virtual keyboard stays on if the popup dialog is dismissed by tapping outside of it while editing.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Tapping `Cancel` or `OK` on the dialog does dismiss the keyboard but not if tapped outside of it.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">/cc @tonyr59h</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
